\pard\f0\fs28  Subgen. {\b Auriculastrum} Schott. Heterostylous. Farinose or efarinose. Hairs glandular, sometimes minute. Leaves with involute vernation, fleshy or coriaceous, not rugose. Bracts not gibbous or saccate. Calyx rounded, not angled.
